contentfulProduct.name: Salmon Paté
contentfulProduct.teaser: Salmon Paté, grainfree, complete and balanced wetfood for adult cats

ingredients.ingredients: 72% fresh meat and meat products, 19% fresh salmon, plant products, vitamins & minerals.

analysis.analysis: Protein 8%, fat content 5%, crude ash 2%,crude fibre 0.2%, moisture 82%.

feedingRecommendation.feedingRecommendation: Freshwater should always be available. Prior to opening the pack,  it should be stored in dry, cool conditions. After opening, store in an airtight container, keep refrigerated and use it within 72 Hours. The recommended quantities can vary according to breed, seasonal and age factors. Traceability: Best before date/lot no, see can bottom.

nutritionAdditives.nutritionAdditives: Vitamin A 1000IU/kg, Vitamin D3 100IU/kg , Vitamin E 10IU/kg, Zinc (Zinc Sulphate Monohydrate) 5 mg/kg, Manganese (Manganous Sulphate Monohydrate) 2,5 mg/kg, Selenium (Sodium Selenite) 0.02 mg/kg, Iodine (Calcium iodate anhydrous) 0.25 mg/kg, Taurine 250 mg/kg.

longDescription.longDescription:
Chef’s Choice Salmon recipe for Adult Cats is formulated by chefs and nutritionists, made with 100% fresh salmon and natural ingredients and is free from grains, sugar, salt, artificial colors, aromas or preservatives. This delicious and nutritious recipe is enhanced with vitamins, minerals and other nutrients to make your cat crave for more! 
You might be cooking your own food but your cat has a Chef at home.
